# Large binary release assets are NOT committed to git. They are staged here on
# the build workstation, pinned by sha256 in proofs/v090/readme_case_manifest.json,
# and uploaded as GitHub release assets at tag time by the manager.
#
# Tracked (small, human-reviewable): the sample namelists + README + this file.
# Ignored (large binaries): the tarball and the NetCDF wrfout/wrfinput/wrfbdy.

*.tgz
*.tar.gz
staging/**/wrfout_*
staging/**/wrfinput_*
staging/**/wrfbdy_*
